AllCoreCPUUsageScreenlet v0.4 (c) 2008 Paul Ashton
http://ashysoft.blogspot.com/

Requirements:
Screenlets 0.0.10 <http://www.screenlets.org/>

How to Install?
Copy the 'AllCoreCPUUsage' folder into your '~/.screenlets' folder and start it from the Screenlets Manager :)

Bugs?
Please report any bugs you find to drashy [at] gmail [dot] com or leave a
comment on my site <http://ashysoft.blogspot.com/>, thanks!

Hope you enjoy the screenlet!
Ashy.

==================================
Update Log:
v0.4
 - Added color options, removed themes (for now)
 - Fixed resizing bug when scale was not 100% (using 100% cpu!)
 - Fixed graph accuracy
 
v0.3
 - Added option to start CPU naming from 1 instead of 0
 - Added theming ability
 - Added some themes, feel free to send your own for inclusion in the next version :)
 - Added text color and shadow options

v0.2
 - New 'Graph' mode
 - Fixed size bug

v0.1
 - First public release.

